Mountains stand out against blue skies and white snow in Hutubi County, northwest China's Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region. In eastern Jiangxi Province, the Wugong Mountains disappear in a sea of clouds, while in neighboring Fujian Province, clouds seem to be growing out of Jinnao Mountain. Enjoy this video from Weather China, the China Meteorological Administration's online weather service. (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)